DataElement.preferredDefinition: A substance made from living organisms or things they produce. EXAMPLE(S): virus, therapeutic serum, toxin, antitoxin, vaccine, blood, blood component or derivative, allergenic product, analogous product A coded value specifying the kind of product. EXAMPLE(S): veterinary medicine, diagnostic device
